=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=
=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=


Italy woke up to find himself lying on the flower beds. He stood up and looked around. "Wh-what am I doing here?I have to go back now! Everyone will get worried--"


"Italy!!" he heard a voice say.



The Italian turned around to find the source of the voice he heard just then....but what he saw made him feel like his blood drained down. "You're..."



A man of a familiar face stood before him and spoke, "I was looking for you, Italy."



Ho....



"Holy Roman Empire."